## 🎯 Why I Chose This Topic

Email marketing delivers the highest ROI of any B2B channel — and it compounds.
Unlike ads or SEO, a well-built newsletter creates a **direct line to decision-makers** that grows stronger over time.

**My reasoning:**
- My background in **corporate training & content development** maps directly to how B2B newsletters educate and nurture leads
- I built an audience from zero with **MPSCWifiStudy** (EdTech, 2010–present) — retention, trust, and consistent value delivery are the same principles
- This is a topic I can **speak to credibly in any interview** and apply immediately in a GTM or Business Development role

